======================================================================

		Zentyal Firewall module by MAC

======================================================================


This module allow [internal] traffic based on MAC for every object member.



1.- Create a Objects and add members with MAC, hostname and IP
    (use 127.1.1.x for members without static address)

2.- Enable module

3.- Watch that you can use internal network if your MAC is registered

4.- zentyal-dhcp package use ISC dhcp3-server that CAN'T be firewalled
    Uninstall it and install dnsmasq for block DHCP traffic.
